OL,3,CDerby watches Britain's biggest bike
OL,4,Crace for the first time in 20 years
OL,6,FSome of the world's top cyclists have
OL,7,Ftravelled far to take part in the
OL,8,Ffourth phase of Britain's biggest bike
OL,9,Frace
OL,11,FIt also marks a historic moment for
OL,12,FDerby Arena as they view the UK's
OL,13,Fbiggest bike race for the first time.
OL,15,FThe men's Tour of Britain has been
OL,16,Frunning for the last 20 years. It
OL,17,Fstarted in Scotland earlier this week
OL,18,Fand now Derby is hosting stage 4 of
OL,19,Fthe race.
