OL,3,CDerby watches Britain's biggest bike
OL,4,Crace for the first time in 20 years
OL,6,FMore than 100 of the world's top
OL,7,Friders are taking part, including
OL,8,FParis 2024 Olympic gold medallists
OL,9,FRemco Evenepoel and Tom Pidcock.
OL,11,FThe Mayor of the East Midlands has
OL,12,Fshared her excitement as the iconic
OL,13,Frace comes to the Midlands.
OL,15,FShe said: "Anybody who sees the race
OL,16,Ftoday will see thousands of people
OL,17,Flining the streets along the route,
OL,18,Fcheering them on, getting into it,
OL,19,Fit's really exciting."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
