OL,3,CDerby watches Britain's biggest bike
OL,4,Crace for the first time in 20 years
OL,6,F"But it's also great for our local
OL,7,Feconomy. It brings people here, it
OL,8,Fshowcases our fantastic region, and it
OL,9,Freally does make a difference."
OL,11,FShe added: "It is inspiring, it's
OL,12,Fexciting and it's the sort of thing
OL,13,Fthat youngsters will remember as they
OL,14,Fgrow up, and I hope it will encourage
OL,15,Fthem to get on their bikes."
OL,17,FThe race started at Derby Arena,
OL,18,Fbefore heading through Elvaston,
OL,19,FBorrowash, West Hallam and Heanor.
