OL,4,Crace for the first time in 20 years
OL,6,FIt will then cross into
OL,7,FNottinghamshire at Eastwood continuing
OL,8,Fthrough Hucknall, Ravenshead,
OL,9,FBlidworth, Southwell and Tuxford,
OL,10,Fbefore crossing the River Trent to
OL,11,Frace south to the finish in Newark-on-
OL,12,FTrent.
OL,14,FDerbyshire Police have released a
OL,15,Fstatement on their website warning of
OL,16,Froad closures and short delays for
OL,17,Fdrivers in these areas.
