OL,4,Crace for the first time in 20 years
OL,6,FThey said: "If you're inspired to get
OL,7,Fout on a bike this weekend it's
OL,8,Fimportant to remember the highway code
OL,9,Fand for cyclists and drivers alike to
OL,10,Flook after each other.
OL,12,FCyclists have a responsibility to ride
OL,13,Fwith respect and use cycle lanes when
OL,14,Favailable. It can be safer to ride
OL,15,Fside by side when riding in a group,
OL,16,Fhowever you should consider moving
OL,17,Finto single file when possible, to
OL,18,Fallow cars to overtake.
